{{Quote|But remember, dwarf, that the Tinnell always catches its T'iin-T'iin.|[[Xim/Legends|Xim]] to [[Oziaf]], in the [[The Cry of the Evocii|third episode]] of the play [[Evocar (play)|''Evocar'']]|<ref name="Evocar">{{Hyperspace|url=fans/hyperspace/source/ximweek05/index.html|text=Xim Week: ''The Despotica'' (Part IV: ''Evocar'')|int=Xim Week: The Despotica}}</ref>}}
The '''Tinnell''' were a [[Feline/Legends|felinoid]] [[Species/Legends|species]] of [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]] from the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]]. While considered naïve, they were master mechanics with the skill to improvise repairs that made things work better than designed.<ref name="BF" />

